snippet.title: MIZ - Myth of the Imaginary Zone: Phase Travelers (Lite) - Beta Test Gameplay
snippet.description:
☕ Donation/Support ☕
Ko-fi (Worldwide): https://ko-fi.com/Gamerhenky
Patreon: https://patreon.com/Gamerhenky
Trakteer (For Indonesia only): https://trakteer.id/Gamerhenky

The game will have both Standard and Full version (app only) once the beta ended in early January (approx ¥1.000 / 6.99 / IDR 109,000.00). The difference between in Lite version / Standard Edition is ads inclusion, any cleared dungeon will be removed, and no New Game+ available.

Play on your Web Browser (Standard only): https://miz-rpg.com

iOS App Store: https://apps.apple.com/jp/app/miz/id1602877338

Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.co.altoterras.miz1

💬 Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/gamerhenky
🐦 Twitter: https://twitter.com/Gamerhenky
🗨️ Discord: https://discord.gg/B24SvymHVU
🌏 Others: https://linktr.ee/Gamerhenky

#drpg #retrogaming #wizardry
